 |coauthors=Daniel T. Jones, and Daniel Roos
 |title=[[The_Machine_That_Changed_the_World_(book)|The Machine That Changed the World]]
 |year=1990
}}</ref><ref name="Holweg 2007 420–437">{{cite journal |last=Holweg |first=Matthias |title=The genealogy of lean production |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-operations-management_2007-03_25_2/page/420 |journal=Journal of Operations Management |volume=25 |issue=2 |pages=420–437 |year=2007 |doi=10.1016/j.jom.2006.04.001}}</ref>丰田生产系统以降低丰田的''{{tsl|en|Muda (Japanese term)|七项浪费}}''、降低浪费、提升整体客户价值而闻名。但达到这个目标的方法有很多。[[丰田|丰田]]多年以来的持续增长，从一个默默无闻的小公司成长为世界最大的汽车制造商。<ref name="Reuters">{{cite news
